title: Full Show (Cowboys win four straight, Brady holds onto win, Lamar beats Burrow on SNF)
description:
00:00 Cowboys beat Rams 22-10 behind Cooper Rush and dominant defense
24:35 Brady and the Bucs hold on to beat the Falcons 21-15 after controversial roughing the passer call
56:48 Lamar beat Burrow and the Bengals 19-17
1:08:47 Dak speaks on the Cowboys potential when he is healthy
1:21:30 Panthers QB Baker Mayfield injured in 37-15 loss to 49ers
1:31:57 The latest Antonio Brown scandal 
1:40:17 Draymond Green takes time away from Warriors after incident with Jordan Poole
1:48:55 Deion Sanders postgame flair up with Alabama State head coach Eddie Robinson Jr.
1:54:31 Aaron Jones weighs in on the Packers loss to the Giants
